dc_title_s: South America, Chile--west coast, plans on the coast of Chile (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. "From Chilean charts." "Copyright 1996 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Map No.22221 Includes tidal information. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
